				OK, heres what I have to say about this quest, and others alike.  Yeah, sure youve found a kickin way to level with no work!  Alright!  Now when you start fighting, you seem to have a problem.  You are missing more than half the time, your spells are taking incredibly long to cast.  Your trade skills...aren't the best.  Sometimes its better just to bite the bullet.  Actually fight monsters...harsh yes, helpful, oh yes.  Yes, I admit, I used the skeleton chip quest in kaladim to get to level 8(hehe, i had over 120 bone chips!!).  You get 5 chances to increase every skill you have per level, use them, don't wast them.<BR>
